abstract: United States military says it destroyed 283 tanker trucks in Syria in operation that is part of effort to cripple Islamic State oil revenues.
lead_paragraph: The United States military said Monday that it had destroyed 283 tanker trucks used by Islamic State militants to transport oil out of eastern Syria.
